main event: Radar targets were observed descending at 1500 feet per minute 50 miles NW of Midway Island.
interesting points: The targets were observed for 19 minutes on radar,Two radar targets were detected at an altitude of 6,000 feet,There was insufficient data for conclusive identification of the objects,Additional investigation was required due to conflicting reports at the time,The sighting did not match characteristics of a balloon.
